# Steam UI Tests

## Check that main page loads
* Navigate to "https://store.steampowered.com"
* Title should contain "Steam"

## Search for Path of Exile 2
* Navigate to "https://store.steampowered.com"
* Write "Path of Exile 2" into the field near "store_nav_search_term"
* Press Enter
* There should be some results

## Go to game page and check Add to Card
* Navigate to "https://store.steampowered.com"
* Write "path of exile 2" into the field near "store_nav_search_term"
* Press Enter
* Click the first result
* Check if button exists (optional, depends on availability)